to create first chart :-
$ helm create firstchart
to check helm charts :-
$ helm ls
to install helm chart :-
$ helm install <release-name> <chart-name>
$ helm install release1 firstchart
if you change anything in charts yamls then use upgrade command :--
$ helm upgrade rlease1 firstchart
if you want to rollback to privious version :-
$ helm rollback <chart name> 1
$ helm rollback firstchart 1
